{"tid":2462289,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教局派中小學教材《我的家在中國》灌民族主義　「香港在祖國懷抱中發達」","createTime":"2021-03-26T02:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T03:31:59.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b756cf7f34d8008f119d90434f74e0724a1ff141","tid":2462289,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ASQv4g58VQRSZ897NtE5JzVGIGY=/802x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LUZ6EBJ53ZAUFLF7MUNYXIRTII.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FASQv4g58VQRSZ897NtE5JzVGIGY%3D%2F802x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLUZ6EBJ53ZAUFLF7MUNYXIRTII.JPG&h=f184b3ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《我的家在中國》全套分6個範疇共48冊，由北京師範大學特聘教授檀傳寶主編。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OAwoqnoiWLvJXVoL8oEvfkZhFfE=/802x1015/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MTHK2ZQARVAY7CS4FTPFLKRG7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOAwoqnoiWLvJXVoL8oEvfkZhFfE%3D%2F802x1015%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMTHK2ZQARVAY7CS4FTPFLKRG7Y.jpg&h=6df84fcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n教材提及台北部份街道「大多以我國地理上的西北城市為名」，是國民政府為了清除日本的影響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yU-da-qVcn7Sxe7eyfw6KAjic_o=/802x1012/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FLKPLUXYVJAKVIEKP2HJQAD7GE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyU-da-qVcn7Sxe7eyfw6KAjic_o%3D%2F802x1012%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFLKPLUXYVJAKVIEKP2HJQAD7GE.jpg&h=59386ce4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該書形容，澳門「被人擄走」，斥葡萄牙1553年起通過「不正當行為」，「一步步蠶食了澳門」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Qp8Lf4vyrSD8M83beKQqDsA9xXg=/802x1026/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TVP4GQ5ZRZBPVGYZOMFRMK22QU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQp8Lf4vyrSD8M83beKQqDsA9xXg%3D%2F802x1026%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTVP4GQ5ZRZBPVGYZOMFRMK22QU.jpg&h=cd0919c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《開往春天的列車──鐵路》提到興建廣深港高鐵爭議，指必須拆掉菜園村才能建高鐵和配套，結果香港政府要大幅提高賠償，令建造費用不菲。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n《蘋果》檢視該書2016年簡體版，書腰列明是「教育部青少年國情教育指定閱讀書目」、「中小學少先隊主題班隊會活動首選用書」，惟暫時未知繁體版與簡體版的內容會是否有分別。少先隊全名「中國少年先鋒隊」，由共青團直接領導，旨在培養少年及兒童成為「共產主義事業的接班人」，標誌是戴紅領巾。中共中央上月發文件提到少先隊要通過交流增強港澳台少年兒童的國家認同。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210326/BUFS4R7IVFFBLBJLSUC6TKGTOY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210326%2FBUFS4R7IVFFBLBJLSUC6TKGTOY%2F&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GgjGR3CVFSgRSSfEWrWQqBA%3D&h=134e1517\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210326%2FBUFS4R7IVFFBLBJLSUC6TKGTOY%2F&h=0c3410d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210326/BUFS4R7IVFFBLBJLSUC6TKGTOY/</a>"},{"pid":"2ddc1e9395550a41851dc64edb859d6fe49ef832","tid":2462289,"uid":49329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:13:06.000Z","msg":"全面洗腦"},{"pid":"d2971b809e772d157ada76a042b6ef85fa68289c","tid":2462289,"uid":114488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:13:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9139e5b288a9eb4f65aec662a3b3cd03ef772ffc","tid":2462289,"uid":145273,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:14:55.000Z","msg":"見到有殘體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma